<emphasis id="9CBE9523FFDCAC5211C0F43CFEB3F8E3" bold="true" box="[164,268,1846,1868]" pageId="10" pageNumber="182">Figure 5.</emphasis>
Photograph and interpretation of the specimen MNHNL TU885 
<taxonomicName id="69CA32B2FFDCAC5212D3F43CFAA9F8E4" authorityName="Laboury &amp; Bennion &amp; Thuy &amp; Weis &amp; Fischer" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Laboury &amp; Bennion &amp; Thuy &amp; Weis &amp; Fischer" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[951,1302,1846,1868]" class="Reptilia" family="Leptopterygiidae" genus="Temnodontosaurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ichthyosauria" pageId="10" pageNumber="182" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zetlandicus">
<emphasis id="9CBE9523FFDCAC5212D3F43CFBC2F8E4" box="[951,1149,1846,1868]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="182">Temnodontosaurus</emphasis>
cf. 
<emphasis id="9CBE9523FFDCAC5215C4F43CFAA9F8E4" box="[1184,1302,1846,1868]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="182">zetlandicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
A, B, in right lateral view. C, D, in dorsal view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="FAB519B9FFDDAC5311F5F60EFABFFA9F" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6536807" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6536807" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6536807/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="183" startId="11.[145,223,1284,1306]" targetBox="[148,1429,198,1241]" targetPageId="11">
<paragraph id="AE754931FFDDAC5311F5F60EFABFFA9F" blockId="11.[145,1425,1284,1335]" pageId="11" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="9CBE9523FFDDAC5311F5F60EFF47FAB1" bold="true" box="[145,248,1284,1306]" pageId="11" pageNumber="183">Figure 6.</emphasis>
Photograph and interpretation of the specimen MNHNL TU885 
<taxonomicName id="69CA32B2FFDDAC5312F9F60EFB45FAB2" authorityName="Laboury &amp; Bennion &amp; Thuy &amp; Weis &amp; Fischer" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Laboury &amp; Bennion &amp; Thuy &amp; Weis &amp; Fischer" baseAuthorityYear="2022" box="[925,1274,1284,1306]" class="Reptilia" family="Leptopterygiidae" genus="Temnodontosaurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ichthyosauria" pageId="11" pageNumber="183" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zetlandicus">
<emphasis id="9CBE9523FFDDAC5312F9F60EFBDCFAB2" box="[925,1123,1284,1306]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="183">Temnodontosaurus</emphasis>
cf. 
